OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784303301
OL,3,CTwo more arrests as moorland fire
OL,4,Ccontinues
OL,6,FTwo more people have been arrested in
OL,7,Fthe ongoing investigation into the
OL,8,Fmoorland fire that has been declared a
OL,9,Fmajor incident.
OL,11,FA 19-year-old woman was arrested on 16
OL,12,FJuly, and has been bailed pending
OL,13,Ffurther police enquiries.
OL,15,FA man in his 20s has also been
OL,16,Farrested on suspicion of arson and
OL,17,Fremains in custody for questioning.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
