OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784303301
OL,3,CTwo more arrests as moorland fire
OL,4,Ccontinues
OL,6,FThree arrests have now been made in
OL,7,Frelation to the Dovestone Reservoir
OL,8,Ffires, after Shania Care-Slede, 20,
OL,9,Fwas charged with aggravated arson on
OL,10,FTuesday, 14 July.
OL,12,FShe will appear at Manchester Crown
OL,13,FCourt on Tuesday, 18 August.
OL,15,FPaul Fearnhead, Greater Manchester
OL,16,FFire and Rescue service said: "There's
OL,17,Fbeen a lot of damage. We've been here
OL,18,Fat Dovestones for about seven days
OL,19,Fnow. That damage has been restricted
OL,20,Fto the area that we could see.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784303301
OL,3,CTwo more arrests as moorland fire
OL,4,Ccontinues
OL,6,F"We've stopped it going into a
OL,7,Fmemorial woodland that is a really
OL,8,Fprecious area to people who frequent
OL,9,Fthis area quite a lot. But the earth
OL,10,Fhas been scorched.
OL,12,F"We've got great resources, great
OL,13,Fteams and great people who are really
OL,14,Fworking hard. That extends to the
OL,15,Flocal community as well."
OL,17,FHe continued: "Currently, this is not
OL,18,Fgoing to be put out anytime soon. We
OL,19,Fneed heavy rain to well this fire.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784303301
OL,3,CTwo more arrests as moorland fire
OL,4,Ccontinues
OL,6,F"We have got resources that are
OL,7,Fpumping large amounts of water around
OL,8,Fthe area which is causing some traffic
OL,9,Fproblems and issues."
OL,11,FDetective Inspector Andrew Day said:
OL,12,F"This investigation has been
OL,13,Fprogressing at pace, we are nearly a
OL,14,Fweek on and the fire at Dovestones is
OL,15,Fstill ongoing, and it has had
OL,16,Fdevastating effects it has had on the
OL,17,FReservoir.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
