PN,36305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784303301
OL,3,CTwo more arrests as moorland fire
OL,4,Ccontinues
OL,6,F"I mentioned in my last update that we
OL,7,Fare aware of the social media posts
OL,8,Fcirculating regarding this incident,
OL,9,Fit is a live police investigation, and
OL,10,FI would like to stress the point
OL,11,Fagain, to stop sharing and speculating
OL,12,Fregarding this and if you do have
OL,13,Finformation, please report it to
OL,14,Fourselves.
OL,16,F"As this incident continues, officers
OL,17,Fwould like to thank all emergency
OL,18,Fservice partners for their support and
OL,19,Fdedication.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
